{
  "stem": "10272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Chust, Chust.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So a junior high--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Secular school.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very well.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no incident in-- no incidents in school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But outside of the school, when I came home-- at that time, even before this crisis of, of Munich in 1938-- it started already in 1934, after Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I noticed, when I went to visit my grandma, which is in Terebla-- she lived with my-- with my sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were under a-- also a grocery and a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] drinking-- serving drinking for people there, alcohol, wine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I was on my bike-- I was riding there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I came to that village inn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In our town, Bustino, I didn't hear no, no, not-- at that time, I came, and they-- I was there as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I dressed as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I looked like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The kids would run from their houses to the-- to the fence and see who is passing by-- oh!",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they start screaming at me and throwing stones and rocks on me and slur-- Jewish slurs, like, Jew, go to Palestine, and all kind of slurs-- 'dirty Jew.' I would hear already at that time from 1935, 1936, 1937, 1938.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in our school, we were only Czech, Czech people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In this area was many ethnic groups where I was part of that area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were Ruthenians, Hungarians, Czechs, and also Romanians, and Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to a Jewish Czech school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were also Hungarian schools and the Ruthenian schools.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many Jewish people entered other schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- all schools acknowledged by the government, Czech government, as legal schools for education.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my father sent me to a Czech school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these boys and girls in the Czech school, we were-- Jewish people were more-- were the majority of the school, see?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were-- there were not so many Czech boys in school-- and girls who went to the school because they came only-- they were sent from Czech Republic to this area, to this area [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to do a job, like, like the state employee be, or working on the train, working in the post office, like these area-- these jobs.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were not-- it's the Czech people are not-- very rarely when somebody is anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe he is in his heart, but he doesn't show it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I didn't know-- and never encountered any Jewish anti-Semitism from a Czech person, never.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For hobbies, I was-- draw my-- to, to draw people, to draw faces, to draw all kinds of things, animals.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I liked to draw with a pencil on a paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once I draw the, the portrait of president-- our president, Masaryk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the teacher send this portrait to the president, to Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got a letter from him that he was very happy to-- that such talented kids in, in-- And I have to mention, also, that this area where I'm from is a unique place on the map-- on the European map.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is not a big area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's the size of, like, New Jersey, let's say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was-- it's changed hands-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so I don't know many-- how many-- how many times.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was under occupation of the Romans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Romans were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then there were the Turkish Empire, the Turks-- under the Turks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then came the, the Russians in World War I.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then it was the Austrian-Hungarian Empire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It belonged to the-- part of that empire was this area, this territory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then in World War II, again-- it was between World War I and World War II the Czech Republic was established.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this territory was, was annexed to the Czech Republic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we were part of Czechoslovakia when I was born.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And during World War II, Hungary occupied this territory-- the Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "After World War II, again, Soviet Union-- it was attached to Soviet Union-- was part of Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And now, it is part of Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Ukraine, she split with Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She became independent.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she took this territory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, and she was-- and she's-- this is part of the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So it's, it's, it's-- it's a very-- many, many ethnic groups are there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in the Czech school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I happened to go to the Czech school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When did things start to change?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When did you--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The anti-Semitism?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you that I noticed it already after the-- Hitler came to the power when I went to village.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In, in our-- in our town, there was no big anti-Semite expressions because-- I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- the people were more, more city-like.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
